  "text": "The quantification of surface immunofluorescence was accomplished by determining the mean fluorescence intensities for cells using Adobe Photoshop as described previously [CITATION_1] . Individual cells were outlined manually using the lasso tool on immunofluorescence pictures opened in Photoshop. The mean fluores-cence values of selected areas were determined with the histogram submenu. Background fluorescence values were obtained from empty vector-transfected cells and were subtracted from the values obtained from cells expressing HN and F proteins.",
